---
title: Almond & Garlic-Crusted Chicken with Roasted Veggie Chunks & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: This is crumbed chicken with a difference. First, it's spread with herbed mayo and then it's topped with a mixture of panko breadcrumbs and chopped roasted almonds. There's no dipping in egg and flour, and the result is a total game changer.
